    <div class='row'>
      <h3>Objective</h3>
      <p>
        To build a responsive
        <strong>React e-commerce experience</strong>
        with clear product browsing, useful search feedback, cart functionality, and a simple
        checkout flow. The focus was to create a small but complete shop interface that feels
        structured, polished, and easy to use.
      </p>
